informationsectionpa.rightContentText:
With FreeStyle Libre, you carry a small sensor on the back of your upper arm that automatically monitors your glucose around the clock 3 .

 

Instead of finger prick 1 , you can simply read the sensor painlessly 2 in one second. Each reading shows a current glucose measurement, a trend arrow and an eight-hour history.
